1
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:30,760
Hello, Mr. Lu.

2
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:34,680
Hello, Mr. Lu.

3
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:39,960
Mr. Lu.

4
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,000
Mr. Lu, about last night,

5
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,120
I want to explain it to you.

6
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,000
Ma'am, you cannot enter this building
without an appointment.

7
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,479
Mr. Lu.

8
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:46,240
Please leave.

9
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,840
I'm not leaving until you see me!

10
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,759
Please leave.

11
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,120
Su Xia?

12
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,880
The elevator is here.

13
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,920
Hello, Jian Xi.

14
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,130
Lu Fan refuses to see me now.

15
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,760
You can't just abandon me now.

16
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,520
You were set up by Su Xia.

17
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,760
You idiot. Can't you even get this right?

18
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:22,680
Jian Xi, I'm trying to help you.

19
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,440
And you're calling me an idiot?

20
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,440
Enough. Stop your act.

21
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,720
Lu Fan won't do anything to you.

22
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,320
Don't contact me for a while.

23
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,720
Hey, Jian Xi.

24
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:49,800
Idiot. Took you long enough.

25
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,640
Han Qi?

26
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,280
Miss Jian.

27
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,680
I thought you didn't recognize me.

28
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,440
You're back in the country,

29
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:16,920
and you didn't even
come see your old friend?

30
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,000
Wait, no.

31
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:21,440
I should call you Mrs. Lu now.

32
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:23,410
Why would I come see you?

33
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,600
Are we that close?

34
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:26,960
You bitch.

35
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,960
Have you forgotten when you begged me

36
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,200
to help your family?

37
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,760
You really think a few years overseas

38
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,090
wiped your slate clean?

39
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,840
What do you want?

40
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,640
What do I want?

41
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,880
I want you to be Mrs. Lu.

42
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,520
Don't be nervous.

43
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,640
I

44
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,800
offended Lu Fan over the cemetery project.

45
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,680
He's driven me to a corner now.

46
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,240
Go talk to him

47
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,450
and ask him to let me off.

48
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,760
I can't interfere with his business.

49
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,560
There's nothing I can do.

50
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,880
Mrs. Lu.

51
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:05,840
I'm sure

52
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:08,080
you remember this thing.

53
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,200
You bastard!

54
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:26,760
Mrs. Lu, I'm sure you'll find a way.

55
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,440
Back then,

56
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,900
you were the one who came
to my bed willingly.

57
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,380
I didn't force you, right?

58
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,480
I'll help you.

59
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:42,090
But you have to wait
after Lu Fan and I get married.

60
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:46,360
I might not be able to hold out that long.

61
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,400
You have to give me time.

62
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:52,080
Before Lu Fan and I officially marry,

63
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,920
nothing and no one

64
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,680
can get in our way.

65
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,440
Understand?

66
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,220
T-Then how about this?

67
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,080
Have Jian Group

68
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:06,480
inject some capital into my company first.

69
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,480
Helping me is helping yourself.

70
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,290
Once I get through this period,

71
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,490
you can secure your place as Mrs. Lu

72
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:16,000
without any worries.

73
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,840
Don't go too far.

74
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,040
I'm not going too far.

75
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:23,320
This money is

76
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:26,720
a drop in the bucket
for the future Mrs. Lu.

77
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,600
Deal.

78
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,560
What else do you want?

79
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,440
Mrs. Lu,

80
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:41,480
you're getting more and more charming.

81
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,680
Let go of me, you bastard!

82
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,720
Let go!

83
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,040
Stop yelling!

84
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,650
Aren't you afraid Lu Fan will hear you?

85
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,640
Lu Fan pushed me

86
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,400
to the edge.

87
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,440
I'm a man, too.

88
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:02,440
I've gotta make him pay somehow.

89
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,640
Don't worry.

90
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,840
This is the last time.

91
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,600
You bastard!

92
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,680
Let go!

93
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,200
Let me go!

94
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,440
Stop playing the innocent girl!

95
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,720
Sir, please.

96
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,520
Where is he?

97
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,280
Mr. Han.

98
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,159
Mr. Han.

99
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,080
Mr. Jian,

100
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,290
what do you want to see me about?

101
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,320
I wouldn't have invited you here

102
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,800
if it weren't for something important.

103
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,880
Sit down and let's talk.

104
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,520
Just say it here.

105
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,880
I'm in a hurry.

106
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,880
Dad.

107
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:09,060
Dad.

108
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,760
This is my daughter,

109
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,440
and also the head of this project.

110
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:15,720
Hello.

111
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,720
Hello, Mr. Han.

112
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,220
What were you saying just now?

113
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,490
Let's take our time.

114
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,240
Please.

115
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,040
Well, introduce it to Mr. Han.

116
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:34,080
Mr. Han, we're having a funding issue

117
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,600
with one of our projects.

118
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,000
Give me three months.

119
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,080
You'll get every penny
of interest you're owed.

120
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:41,080
Could you help us out?

121
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:53,960
I heard Jian Group is backed by Mr. Lu.

122
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,720
And yet you're still coming
to me for money?

123
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,240
Mr. Han,

124
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,120
to be honest,

125
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:02,920
this project was introduced by Mr. Lu.

126
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,520
Now, there's a little problem,

127
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,480
and we

128
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:10,010
don't really want to bother him again.

129
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:12,920
Got it.

130
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,880
You want this project

131
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:17,040
to look good in front of Mr. Lu.

132
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,680
You are indeed a wise man.

133
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:28,400
It seems Mr. Jian has great ambitions.

134
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,640
Then give us a straight answer.

135
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,000
Well.

136
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,559
I'll discuss it with finance

137
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,440
and give you a reply tonight.

138
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,560
Mr. Han is upstairs.

139
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:56,160
Go up, and I'll have finance
release the funds.

140
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,920
I advise you to think it through.

141
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,560
Who are you?

142
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,680
You...

143
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,600
You've got some moves.

144
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,200
I was wrong. Please spare me.

145
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,460
I'll never do it again.

146
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,040
I'll never do it again.

147
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:25,370
I was wrong. I was wrong.

148
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:44,580
I made it through three hours.

149
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:45,720
One careless mistake,

150
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,120
and you could get killed.

151
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,450
I've already died once.

152
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:11,080
Are you here to thank me?

153
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,120
You fight so well.

154
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:16,330
So you were just pretending
to be weak last night?

155
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,760
Last night, it was you who ordered

156
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:19,240
Ms. Wu and the bodyguards

157
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:20,680
to corner me in the restroom

158
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,760
and try to drown me.

159
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,040
Well,

160
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:26,800
you guys used to do this all the time
in high school.

161
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:28,440
You guys dislike me

162
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,220
and can't stand me.

163
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,090
But I saved your life today.

164
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,680
You should at least say thank you.

165
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:51,560
If I do this,

166
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,880
will Lu Fan believe
I was the one who saved him?

167
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:56,120
I have arranged everything.

168
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,720
Only if you do this

169
00:11:58,160 --> 00:12:00,360
will the family fully back your marriage

170
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,840
into the Lu family.

171
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,610
For the Jian family,

172
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,600
and for yourself,

173
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,920
you must do this.

174
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:27,120
Xi.

175
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:29,480
Xi.

176
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:34,800
Xi.

177
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,020
Dad.

178
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:40,080
I want this scar.
